{"tid":1280131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[補習名師]","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T01:00:44.000Z","uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd824c7537d89d633aa038b6cfa782a456c1022c","tid":1280131,"uid":171046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:00:44.000Z","msg":"已經退出補習界、曾經頗有名氣的英文補習導師范浩揚（K.Oten）近年是非多多，與前僱主對簿公堂後，最終因為未能償還賠款破產收場；曾經在事業上助他不少的前妻吳嘉欣（Cher），亦因為背負二人分開前開設的多間公司債務，現在揹上一身債，早前在社交網與友人狂呻，更以「賤男系列」為題貼文，指K.Oten不肯歸還公司名下車輛，最後報警才能解決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SCEXJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SCEXJb.png&h=97bf85b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQaK8PS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQaK8PS.png&h=fe700dff&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}